---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import TetrisHeader from '../components/TetrisHeader.astro';
---

<Layout title="Val's Thoughts - About">
	<TetrisHeader />
	<main>
		<h2>About Val</h2>
		<p>
			Val is a seasoned technologist with years of experience in the ever-evolving world of tech. 
			With a passion for innovation and a keen eye for emerging trends, Val shares insights, 
			thoughts, and musings on various aspects of technology through this blog.
		</p>
		<p>
			From artificial intelligence and web development to cybersecurity and beyond, 
			Val's blog covers a wide range of topics, offering a unique perspective shaped by 
			years of hands-on experience and continuous learning.
		</p>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	main {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}
	h2 {
		font-size: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}
	p {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}
</style>